01101 void testBinaryDataOnly()
01102 {
01103     MSData tiny;
01104     examples::initializeTiny(tiny);
01105 
01106     MSData tinier;
01107     SpectrumListSimplePtr sl(new SpectrumListSimple);
01108     ChromatogramListSimplePtr cl(new ChromatogramListSimple);
01109     tinier.run.spectrumListPtr = sl; 
01110     tinier.run.chromatogramListPtr = cl; 
01111 
01112     for (unsigned int i=0; i<tiny.run.spectrumListPtr->size(); i++)
01113     {
01114         SpectrumPtr from = tiny.run.spectrumListPtr->spectrum(i, true);
01115         sl->spectra.push_back(SpectrumPtr(new Spectrum));
01116         SpectrumPtr& to = sl->spectra.back();   
01117 
01118         for (vector<BinaryDataArrayPtr>::const_iterator it=from->binaryDataArrayPtrs.begin();
01119              it!=from->binaryDataArrayPtrs.end(); ++it)
01120         {
01121             // copy BinaryDataArray::data from tiny to tinier
01122             to->binaryDataArrayPtrs.push_back(BinaryDataArrayPtr(new BinaryDataArray));
01123             to->binaryDataArrayPtrs.back()->data = (*it)->data;
01124         }
01125 
01126         // copy "important" scan metadata
01127 
01128         to->index = from->index;
01129         to->nativeID = from->nativeID;
01130         to->defaultArrayLength = from->defaultArrayLength;
01131 
01132         to->spectrumDescription.precursors.resize(from->spectrumDescription.precursors.size());
01133         for (size_t precursorIndex=0; precursorIndex<from->spectrumDescription.precursors.size(); ++precursorIndex)
01134         {
01135             Precursor& precursorTo = to->spectrumDescription.precursors[precursorIndex];
01136             Precursor& precursorFrom = from->spectrumDescription.precursors[precursorIndex];
01137             precursorTo.selectedIons = precursorFrom.selectedIons;
01138         }
01139     }
01140 
01141     for (unsigned int i=0; i<tiny.run.chromatogramListPtr->size(); i++)
01142     {
01143         ChromatogramPtr from = tiny.run.chromatogramListPtr->chromatogram(i, true);
01144         cl->chromatograms.push_back(ChromatogramPtr(new Chromatogram));
01145         ChromatogramPtr& to = cl->chromatograms.back();   
01146 
01147         for (vector<BinaryDataArrayPtr>::const_iterator it=from->binaryDataArrayPtrs.begin();
01148              it!=from->binaryDataArrayPtrs.end(); ++it)
01149         {
01150             // copy BinaryDataArray::data from tiny to tinier
01151             to->binaryDataArrayPtrs.push_back(BinaryDataArrayPtr(new BinaryDataArray));
01152             to->binaryDataArrayPtrs.back()->data = (*it)->data;
01153         }
01154 
01155         // copy "important" scan metadata
01156 
01157         to->index = from->index;
01158         to->nativeID = from->nativeID;
01159         to->defaultArrayLength = from->defaultArrayLength;
01160     }
01161 
01162     if (os_)
01163     {
01164         *os_ << "tinier::";
01165         TextWriter(*os_,0)(tinier);
01166     }
01167 
01168     Diff<MSData> diff_full(tiny, tinier);
01169     unit_assert(diff_full);
01170 
01171     DiffConfig config;
01172     config.ignoreMetadata = true;
01173 
01174     Diff<MSData> diff_data(tiny, tinier, config);
01175     if (os_ && diff_data) *os_ << diff_data << endl;
01176     unit_assert(!diff_data);
01177 }
